                        <interp inst="t18450707-1473-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 17.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy.—
<rs id="t18450707-1473-punishment-18" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18450707-1473-punishment-18" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
