                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1473-18450707 t18450707-1473-punishment-18"></join>Confined Two Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(There was another indictment against the prisoner.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Williams.</hi>
